</div>
<div style="visibility:hidden">
<div><a href="/wiki/File:Extinction_intensity.svg" title="File:Extinction intensity.svg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/06/Extinction_intensity.svg/320px-Extinction_intensity.svg.png" width="320" height="195" border="0" usemap="#ImageMap_1_137418472" /></a><map name="ImageMap_1_137418472" id="ImageMap_1_137418472">
